<HEADLINE> Israelis, Palestinians Meet Albright for Peace Talks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, November 3 (Xinhua) -- Israeli and Palestinian
negotiators today met with U.S. Secretary of State Madeleine
Albright at the start of a new round of negotiations in an attempt
to pull the peace process in the Middle East back on track.
</P>
<P>
