<HEADLINE> Better Ideological Work Called for </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 4 (Xinhua) -- A top Chinese publicity
official called for efforts to improve ideological work to unite
the whole people for the realization of the tasks set forth by the
15th National Congress of the Communist Party of China (CPC).
</P>
<P>
Ding Guangen, head of the Propaganda Department of the CPC
Central Committee, told a forum organized by the "Fortnight
Review" Magazine that the Party has a fine tradition of doing
ideological work among the people.
</P>
