must place ideological work above anything else because effective
ideological work will ensure the success in reforms and opening
up," Ding said.
</P>
<P>
He stressed ideological work should focus on solving
practical problems with which people are concerned.
</P>
<P>
"Officials doing ideological work should respect and understand
people, and care about the well-being of the people," Ding said.
</P>
<P>
He expressed the hope that the Fortnight Review Magazine will
do a better job in guiding the orientation of the public opinion,
and serving the people and the central task of the Party and the
country.
</P>
<P>
Fortnight Review, a news magazine published by Xinhua New
Agency, has a circulation of more than five million. 
