<P>
BEIJING, November 4 (Xinhua) -- Buhe, vice-chairman of the
Standing Committee of the Chinese National People's Congress
(NPC), met here today with a Colombian Congressional delegation
led by Jorge Lozano, vice-president of the Constitutional
Committee of the Colombian House of Representatives.
</P>
