<HEADLINE> OPEC Oil Prices Continue to Fall </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA, November 3 (Xinhua) -- The average price of OPEC's
basket of seven crudes fell to 19.11 U.S. dollars per barrel last
week, 19 U.S. cents down from the previous week, the Vienna-based
OPEC Secretariat announced today.
</P>
<P>
The average price in October stood at 19.49 U.S. dollars per
barrel, lower than OPEC's benchmark price of 21 U.S. dollars a
barrel. 
</P>
